{{noteTA|G1=物理學}}
'''X(3872)''' 是一種不尋常的粒子，其質量為3871.68 MeV/c<sup>2</sup> <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pdglive.lbl.gov/ |title=Particle Data Group Live listings |access-date=2022-05-19 |archive-date=2013-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622184243/http://pdglive.lbl.gov/ }}</ref>，而它的[[量子数|量子数]]並不符合[[夸克模型|夸克模型]]。該粒子於2003年被[[日本|日本]]的[[Belle實驗|Belle實驗]]<ref>{{Cite journal|doi = 10.1103/PhysRevLett.91.262001|title = Observation of a Narrow Charmoniumlike State in Exclusive B±→K±π+π-J/ψ Decays|journal = Physical Review Letters|volume = 91|issue = 26|year = 2003|last1 = Choi|first1 = S. -K.|last2 = Olsen|first2 = S.|last3 = Abe|first3 = K.|last4 = Abe|first4 = T.|last5 = Adachi|first5 = I.|last6 = Ahn|first6 = B.|last7 = Aihara|first7 = H.|last8 = Akai|first8 = K.|last9 = Akatsu|first9 = M.|last10 = Akemoto|first10 = M.|last11 = Asano|first11 = Y.|last12 = Aso|first12 = T.|last13 = Aulchenko|first13 = V.|last14 = Aushev|first14 = T.|last15 = Bakich|first15 = A.|last16 = Ban|first16 = Y.|last17 = Banerjee|first17 = S.|last18 = Bondar|first18 = A.|last19 = Bozek|first19 = A.|last20 = Bračko|first20 = M.|last21 = Brodzicka|first21 = J.|last22 = Browder|first22 = T.|last23 = Chang|first23 = P.|last24 = Chao|first24 = Y.|last25 = Chen|first25 = K. -F.|last26 = Cheon|first26 = B.|last27 = Chistov|first27 = R.|last28 = Choi|first28 = Y.|last29 = Choi|first29 = Y.|last30 = Danilov|first30 = M.}}</ref>團隊首次發現，並已被多個其他的實驗團隊所確認。有數種理論被提出以解釋它的性質，例如{{le|介子分子模型|mesonic molecule}}或{{le|雙夸克|diquark}}-反雙夸克對（[[四夸克态|四夸克态]]）模型<ref>Eric S. Swanson,  [http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0370157306001475 The new heavy mesons: A status report] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0370157306001475 |date=20150924172649 }}, ''Physics Reports'', Volume 429, Issue 5, July 2006, Pages 243–305</ref>。

X(3872) 的量子數已於2013年3月被[[歐洲核子研究組織|歐洲核子研究組織]]的[[LHCb|LHCb]]實驗測得，其[[總角動量量子數|J]]<sup>[[宇稱|P]][[電荷共軛對稱|C]]</sup>的值為1<sup>++</sup><ref>[[arxiv:arXiv:1302.6269|LHCb collaboration: Determination of the X(3872) meson quantum numbers]]</ref>。

== 簡介 ==
X(3872)是於2013年由[[Belle實驗|Belle實驗]]團隊在[[B介子|B<sup>±</sup>]] → [[K介子|K<sup>±</sup>]] [[Π介子|π<sup>+</sup>]]π<sup>−</sup>[[J/ψ介子|J/ψ]]衰變模式中發現的，其結果隨後並被多個實驗團隊（如CDF、D0與[[BaBar實驗|BaBar]]團隊）所確認。其後，BABAR和Belle實驗團隊發現了X(3872) → [[光子|γ]] J/ψ衰變模式，確認了X(3872)是一個雙[[魅夸克|魅夸克]]態（c-even state）<ref name="PRL2014">{{cite journal|title=Observation of e<sup>+</sup>e<sup>−</sup> → γX(3872) at BESIII|author=M. Ablikim et al.|journal=Physical Review Letters|date=2014-03-07|volume=112|issue=9|url=http://journals.aps.org/prl/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevLett.112.092001|access-date=2016-09-05|archive-date=2022-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220420025540/https://journals.aps.org/prl/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevLett.112.092001}}</ref><ref name="PRD">{{cite journal|title=Using the decay ψ(4160) → X(3872)γ to probe the molecular content of the X(3872)|author1=Margaryan, Arman|author2=Springer, Roxanne P.|journal=Physical Review D|volume=88|issue=1|date=July 2013|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2013PhRvD..88a4017M}}</ref>。由於X(3872)並未被發現具有χ<sub>c1</sub>γ、χ<sub>c2</sub>γ、以及J/ψ η等末態，它被推測並不是可用簡單夸克模型描述的傳統qq ̄介子態<ref name="PRL2011">{{cite journal|title=Observation of X(3872) → J/ψγ and search for X(3872) → ψ′γ in B decays|author=Bhardwaj V et al.|journal=Physical Review Letters|date=2011-08-26|volume=107|issue=9|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21929226|access-date=2016-09-05|archive-date=2016-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002102618/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21929226}}</ref>。

X(3872)的質量約為3871.5 ± 0.2 MeV/c<sup>2</sup> ，接近[[D介子|D<sup>∗</sup>0]] D0的質量下限，因此X(3872)是一個DD<sup>∗</sup>分子的優良候選。不過，X(3872)也被認為可能是[[四夸克態|四夸克態]]，ccg混合介子態，或者是向量[[膠球|膠球]]模型所描述的那樣<ref name="PRL2014"/>。

X(3872) → J/ψ γ衰變確認了X(3872)的[[宇稱|宇稱]]值為+1。根據最新LHCb團隊的研究結果，X(3872) → ψ′ γ的分支比幾乎是X(3872) → J/ψ γ的三倍，與D<sup>∗</sup>0 D0分子模型並不吻合，而是可以被解釋為cc<sup>-</sup> D<sup>∗</sup>0 D0的混合態<ref name="PRL2011"/>。

